title: The Real Housewives Of Orange County S10E21 Reunion Part 2 WEB-D
description: On part two of the reunion, the ladies look back at the best OMG moments of season 10. Shannon faces scrutiny about her marriage and David's affair, tensions rise when Heather gets heated about Vicki's betrayal of Tamra. Jim Edmonds also joins the ladies on the couch and is put in the hot seat. Briana makes an appearance and is no holds barred when it comes to her opinions about Brooks
